  "description": [
    "THE TIMES PUBLISHED WEEKLY BY J E JONES 2 A YEAR Advertising Rates made known on application Entered at the postoffice at Washburn Wisconsin as secondclass mail matter Washburn Wis Oct 4 99 THE RETURN OF DEWEY If Dewey isnt having a good time it is no fault of the American people The hero returned last week and since that time has been the receiptient of grand and con tinuous ovation New York city went wild with enthusiasm and the whole city turned out to do him honor The great naval parade in his honor was one of the greatest events that has ever occured in New York harbor From New York the hero of Manilla Bay went to Washington where he was enter tained at the White House and re ceived the sword voted him by Con gress and in addition to all this the people want to run the admiral for president of the United States But while the admiral is a good sailor he would perhaps hesitate at Running for so great an office It is altogether likely that the Admiral will be able to give the administra tion some valuable pointers as to how to straighten"
  ],
